source.name: RSS Feeds for Tsunami Advisories in the mainland US, Canada, Alaska, and Puerto Rico/Virgin Islands
source.description: The  National Weather  Service (NWS)  West Coast and Alaska Tsunami Warning Center uses regularly updated RSS feed to disseminate tsunami information statements for US and Canadian Atlantic, and Gulf of Mexico coastal regions.
